Lacrimosa Live (Original from "Stolzes Herz" 1996 EP)  
  Ich bin der brennende Komet (live)  
  *(Tilo Wolff, Anne Nurmi, Jay P, Sascha Gerbig, AC, J Kustner)*  
  
  *^  - hammer on, pull off                   Great song. I tabbed some Keyboard*  
  *b  - bend string up                        parts because they are really useful*  
  *r  - release bend                          to catch the timing and the song as*  
  */  - slide up                              a whole.*  
  *\  - slide down                            Some parts that are repeated throughout*  
  *~  - vibrato                               the song are marked with FIG_, so*  
  *t  - tap (with strumming hand)             some parts have the number of the*  
  *x  - struck string                         figure and the times it will be*  
  *.  - play the note and then mute it        played.*  
  *PM - palm mute                             Something else: almost all rhythms*  
  *AH - Artificial Harmonic                   change constantly, so hear the song*  
    *several times and catch the correct*  
    *one, this is only a guide.*  
  
