  *===============================================================================*  
  *The part that follows is weird to play, but I believe it is the correct form.*  
  *The pick is used for tapping, for sliding and for hammering on(quite difficult)*  
  *Ex:*  
  *-First 8 is played*  
  *-Then the pick taps on 12 and slides to 13 (T/)*  
  *-Then the pick is released so 8 can sound again*  
  *-Again the pick taps on 12 and slides to 13... and so on*  
  *-The resulting sound is something like if played like this:*  
  [e|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|  
