Lacrimosa Live (Original from "Inferno" 1995)  
  Lacrimosa Theme (live)  
  *(Tilo Wolff, Anne Nurmi, Jay P, Sascha Gerbig, AC, J Kustner)*  
  
  */   - slide up*  
  *( ) - chords behind the main melody*  
  *~   - let the note sound*  
  
  *This is the main theme Lacrimosa plays*  
  *in their live presentations, it is played*  
  *by the keyboards but I tabbed it for a*  
  *guitar because it is really a great*  
  *melody. This is the first Lacrimosa tab*  
  *I make. As I realised there was nothing*  
  *in the web about Lacrimosa and their*  
  *music, I spent my entire vacations tabbing*  
  *all the Live album and I hope my work*  
  *turns out to be useful for those Lacrimosa*  
  *fans. Enjoy!*  
  
  *INTRO: keyboard*  
  
